  "texts": [
    "By improving the accuracy and practicality of Chinese dialect emotion recognition, we can further promote the development of related applications in terms of intelligence and humanization.",
    "(5) Multi-dialect recognition: With the rapid economic development and significant population mobility, there is a growing demand for speech recognition systems capable of processing multiple dialects.",
    "Consequently, future research should focus on developing multi-dialect speech recognition systems to support the voice wake-up and recognition of various dialects.",
    "For instance, Wan et al. (2022) analyzed 10 Chinese dialects and constructed a multi-dialect speech recognition system based on deep neural networks.",
    "The system adopts a multi-task learning model assisted by dialect region, which reduces network complexity and enhances recognition accuracy compared to a singletask model."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "For instance, Wan et al. (2022) analyzed 10 Chinese dialects and constructed a multi-dialect speech recognition system based on deep neural networks."
  ]
